Class EndpointAnnotationValidator<T extends java.lang.annotation.Annotation>

    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Validatable

    public class EndpointAnnotationValidator<T extends java.lang.annotation.Annotation>
extends AnnotationValidator<T>
    AnnotationValidator implementation for Lighter Endpoint Annotations. Currently Get, Post, Delete, Put. These annotation types can be validated as a single validator since they all act as an identifier for the same thing.
